cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR 

Reasoning: The paper deals with parsing instructional videos using both visual and language cues, which suggests that it could belong to multiple sub-categories. The use of visual cues indicates that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision), while the use of language cues suggests that it could belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). The joint generative model used in the paper also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The evaluation of the method on a large number of YouTube videos suggests that it could belong to cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
